{"tid":2136241,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"惠譽下調美國主權評級展望至負面","createTime":"2020-08-02T04:13:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T09:35:40.000Z","uid":1086,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a48e4437c6c623d83750ab5df2a547f8b5c6f12b","tid":2136241,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T04:13:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2020/08/01/2538278_4a0c013cc5446d884f939f90b0eb6b3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2020%2F08%2F01%2F2538278_4a0c013cc5446d884f939f90b0eb6b3c.jpg&h=60929500&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n評級機構惠譽公布，確認美國的債務評級為「AAA」，但展望從「穩定」下調至「負面」，理由是公共財政狀況持續惡化，以及缺乏可靠的財政整頓計劃。<br />\n<br />\n惠譽表示，即使在新冠肺炎疫情引發巨大的經濟衝擊之前，美國龐大的財政赤字和債務就已經處於中期上升的軌道上。<br />\n<br />\n該評級機構預計，到2021年，美國的一般政府債務預計將超過GDP(國內生產總值)的130%。美國是所有「AAA」級主權國家中政府債務最高的國家。<br />\n<br />\n惠譽表示，預計美國2020年GDP將萎縮5.6%。美國政府財政形勢正在惡化，預計整體政府債務占GDP比重到2021年將超過130%，預算赤字占GDP比重到2021年料將收窄至11%。<br />\n<br />\n惠譽預計，2021年美國經濟將恢復4%的增速。美國通脹率將保持在較低水準，2020-2022年的平均通脹率將低於1%。"},{"pid":"a476efe40169409b117ce15a007d414db2c16a50","tid":2136241,"uid":23923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T04:14:17.000Z","msg":"帽事既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20d5271f94b699785b67a93c3fafe638716dfa9b","tid":2136241,"uid":159448,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T06:31:15.000Z","msg":"只要軍備夠就可以打橫行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"051d6591ea8272cc9e2c7c0f301ece1e28256014","tid":2136241,"uid":52594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T06:33:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />贏國又贏，最多美國債"},{"pid":"3bd30fe93aff1601e1558c55b59de6fe123374e0","tid":2136241,"uid":23672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T06:45:05.000Z","msg":"星期一老美會唔會千跌 定繼續信政府唔怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ce0c452d5376fb62c4a94d5b30f8839c0da2216","tid":2136241,"uid":140182,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3bd30fe93aff1601e1558c55b59de6fe123374e0","tid":2136241,"uid":23672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T06:45:05.000Z","msg":"星期一老美會唔會千跌 定繼續信政府唔怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T07:42:41.000Z","msg":"壞消息 升 !! <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47e84dd3da8968f4d9207c4e10f6206c306be280","tid":2136241,"uid":113952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T09:35:40.000Z","msg":"當你再睇下佢比中國既評級，睇完只會得啖笑<br />\n次按個陣已經知呢D Credit rating 只係opinions"}]}